data.description: Welcome to Neshaminy Valley Neighborhood !!! This is a Very Unique and rare find and a builder's dream house with 6 Bedroom and 2 Full Bath Single with a large airy basement. This home has a gigantic rear yard sitting on 1 acre of land with nice size swimming pool.  All of rear yard is fenced in. This house was fully updated a year ago including new white kitchen cabinets and modern backsplash , newer updated bathrooms , newer windows , Brand New  Heat & AC Units installed along with newer hot water heater and Central System! You'll Also Love the modern laminated flooring throughout the house & Recessed Lighting .  Huge Driveway up to 8 cars! The list just goes on and on. You have to see it to believe!!!This home will not last long - Make your appointment today! This home is central and easily commutable with access to all major throughways, Mall , Schools, Shopping Centers! MAKE THIS YOUR NEW HOME TODAY!!
